1.0.name: wordpress/upcoming-ticketsolve-shows
1.0.description: Ticketsolve is an online box office system for selling event tickets. This plugin parses the public XML feed from any account on that system and produces a simple list of upcoming shows that you can display in your Worpdress blog.
